{
  "texts": [
    "Notably, the DeepDDS model outperforms SDCNet in leave-one-drug-out evaluation, likely because DeepDDS's performance isn't heavily reliant on the training data.",
    "Conversely, in leave-one-cell-line-out evaluation, SDCNet excels.",
    "This is because SDCNet processes features individually for each cell line, considering the interaction type of medicinal compounds (synergistic or antagonistic).",
    "Overall, SDCNet's success is attributed to its specialized feature processing for different cell lines.",
